{"tid":190503,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《鋼之鍊金術師》真人版電影 預告影片","createTime":"2017-04-07T07:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T03:03:42.000Z","uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b92300e7900b4c37e787c22c26c41ef5d362d49","tid":190503,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"由荒川弘所著的漫畫《鋼之鍊金術師》改編真人版電影，近日釋出了作品的第 2 部預告影片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/74/0001530474.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F74%2F0001530474.JPG&h=83a99806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/75/0001530475.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F75%2F0001530475.JPG&h=98e118c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/76/0001530476.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F76%2F0001530476.JPG&h=b538998a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《鋼之鍊金術師》的舞台設定在一個鍊金術相當發達的世界。在這個世界的鍊金術是必須按照「等價交換」來理解、分解、再構造成立。在這背景之下，想讓母親復活的愛德跟阿爾兩兄弟，使用了禁忌的人體鍊金術。但由於鍊成失敗使得愛德失去了左腳，阿爾失去了身體。於是愛德犧牲了右手，將阿爾的靈魂安置在盔甲裡，而後為了取回失去的東西，他們決定踏上尋找「賢者之石」的旅程。<br />\n<br />\n這次所釋出的預告影片中，可看見年幼時期的愛德跟阿爾兩兄弟登場，而在原作開頭中他們進行人體鍊金術的橋段、以及兩人與魔物戰鬥的場面，也可於本次的預告影片中率先窺探。<br />\n<br />\n《鋼之鍊金術師》真人版電影，預定將於 12 月 1 日在日本上映。<br />\n<br />\n預告1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ifn-qo_yXMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Difn-qo_yXMU&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGojCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=75f007e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ifn-qo_yXMU</a><br />\n<br />\n預告2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oZhOVnowpAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoZhOVnowpAM&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGojCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e50ab4a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oZhOVnowpAM</a>"},{"pid":"51950a8d67cdbbd2905f93b024bff6a3dede51bd","tid":190503,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c35e57933149c2391b4c72d25713ec3f23cb5e","tid":190503,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"山田涼介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6927825e2f99bb7ed9b83e269523b01f8fcc4b6b","tid":190503,"uid":861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:33:22.000Z","msg":"電影劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Uq5sW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Uq5sW3.jpg&h=3f490647&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/07/153304_d541ca03927f08975d6d921d7b597b44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2F153304_d541ca03927f08975d6d921d7b597b44.jpg&h=1d4bf9e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13022a7b0b770e38e8ec16605ce798b44114109d","tid":190503,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"究竟D日本動漫真人版電影可唔可以重新設計下D造型先拍<br />\n基本上個造型一唔係真實系就肯定出事<br />\nCOSPLAY咩屌"},{"pid":"90f385a21de24b21ee275cfe4a492fb21bcf7556","tid":190503,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟D日本動漫真人版電影可唔可以重新設計下D造型先拍<br />\n基本上個造型一唔係真實系就肯定出事<br />\nCOSPLAY咩屌</blockquote><br />\n呢樣美國個邊做得好好多<br />\n美漫大部份造型真人既話一定柒到仆街<br />\n但係電影版改一改 個個造型都靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻哥斯拉一對比<br />\n就知美國個隻霸氣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbce2046404ed8465de4e7dcc393032734217963","tid":190503,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited